metadata.name: Slight Renaissance 1/1
metadata.description:
A researched inventory of lesser-known mechanical marvels intertwines vintage embellishment in full manifest. Messy eccentricities of pre-owned items. Imminently wearable, entirely transformative. Casual pistachio panel lace floral printed cami top, wrap around tie-waist red lace skirt, silky sheen pearl pendant. 

Synth Graph: a center front view, close up, 2020, photograph of a beautiful young 24 year old female model wearing a red lace dress, pink lipstick, cute green purses, crystal earrings and an orange bandana, walking down Manhattan in the 1990s, highly detailed. Sampler: plms, steps: 75, scale: 11.
